anding Performance by a Cast in a Motion Picture|Screen Actors Guild Award for <br>Outstanding Performance by a Cast in a Motion Picture]]\n|-\n|rowspan=4|2002\n| ''[[Sabretooth (film)|Sabretooth]]'' \n| Anthony Bricklin\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Endangered Species (2002 film)|Endangered Species]]'' \n| Police Lt. Wyznowski\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Scorcher (film)|Scorcher]]'' \n| Dr. Matthew Sallin\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers]]''\n|rowspan=2| Gimli <hr> [[Treebeard]]<br>(voice)\n|\n* Phoenix Film Critics Society Award for Best Cast\n* Nominated\u2014[[Screen Actors Guild Award for Outstanding Performance by a Cast in a Motion Picture|Screen Actors Guild Award for<br> Outstanding Performance by a Cast in a Motion Picture]]\n|-\n|rowspan=4|2003\n| ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King]]'' \n| \n*[[Broadcast Film Critics Association Award for Best Cast]]\n*[[National Board of Review Award for Best Cast]]<br>[[Online Film Critics Society Award for Best Cast]]\n* [[Screen Actors Guild Award for Outstanding Performance by a Cast in a Motion Picture|Screen Actors Guild Award for <br>Outstanding Performance by a Cast in a Motion Picture]]\n* Nominated\u2014Phoenix Film Critics Society Award for Best Cast\n|-\n| ''[[Coronado (2003 film)|Coronado]]'' \n| Pres. Ramos\n| \n|- \n| ''[[The Jungle Book 2]]'' \n| Ranjan's father<br> (voice)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Medallion]]''\n| Cmdr. Hammerstock-Smythe\n| \n|-\n|rowspan=5|2004\n| ''[[12 Days of Terror]]''\n| Captain\n| \n|- \n| ''[[The Princess Diaries 2: Royal Engagement]]''\n| Viscount Mabrey\n| \n|-\n| ''[[La Femme Musketeer]]'' \n| Porthos\n| \n|- \n| ''The Lost Angel'' \n| Father Kevin\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Privileged Planet]]'' \n| Narrator (voice)\n| \n|-\n|rowspan=3|2005\n| ''[[The Game of Their Lives (2005 film)|The Game of Their Lives]]''  \n| Bill Jeffrey \n| \n|- \n| ''[[Chupacabra: Dark Seas]]''\n| Capt. Randolph\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The King Maker]]''\n| Phillippe\n| \n|-\n|rowspan=3|2006||''[[Shark Bait]]''|| Thorton (voice) ||English Dub\n|-\n| ''[[One Night with the King]]''\n| Mordecai\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Legend of Sasquatch]]'' \n| Ranger Steve (voice)\n|\n|-\n|rowspan=3|2007\n| ''[[In the Name of the King: A Dungeon Siege Tale]]''\n| Merick\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Ferryman (2007 film)|The Ferryman]]'' \n| The Greek\n| \n|-\n| ''Catching Kringle''\n| Santa <br>(voice)\n|\n|-\n|rowspan=2|2009\n| ''[[Reclaiming the Blade]]''\n| Narrator (voice)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[31 North 62 East]]'' \n| John Hammond\n| \n|-\n|rowspan=2|2010\n| ''Medium Raw: Night of the Wolf''\n| Elliot Carbon\n| TV Movie\n|- \n| ''[[Tom and Jerry Meet Sherlock Holmes]]'' \n| [[Dr. Watson]] (voice) \n| Direct-to-video\n|-\n|rowspan=3|2011\n| ''[[KJB: The Book That Changed the World]]''\n|\n| \n|-\n| ''Sophie and Sheba''\n|\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Ferocious Planet]]''\n| Sen. Crenshaw\n|\n|-\n| 2012\n| ''Escape''\n| Malcolm Andrews\n| \n|-\n|rowspan=3|2013\n| ''100 Degrees Below Zero''\n| Ralph Dillard\n| \n|-\n|''[[Scooby-Doo! Adventures: The Mystery Map]]''||Gnarlybeard (voice) || Direct-to-video\n|-\n| ''[[Prisoners of the Sun (film)|Prisoners of the Sun]]'' \n| Prof. Hayden Masterton\n| \n|-\n|rowspan=3|2014\n| ''[[Apocalypse Pompeii]]''\n| Col. Dillard\n|\n|-\n| ''Saul: The Journey to Damascus''\n| Caiphas\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Prophet (2014 film)|The Prophet]]''\n| Yousef<br>(voice)\n|\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[Beyond the Mask]]''<ref>[http://beyondthemaskmovie.com ''Beyond the Mask'' - Official Website], January 2015.</ref>\n| Charles Kemp\n|\n|-\n|2016\n|''[[The Apostle Peter: Redemption]]''\n|[[Saint Peter]]\n|\n|-\n|2017\n|''[[Shemira]]''\n|[[Myer]]\n|\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''[[Aquaman (film)|Aquaman]]''\n| Brine King<br>(voice)\n|\n|-\n|2019\n| ''[[The Pilgrim's Progress (film)|The Pilgrim's Progress]]''\n| Evangelist (voice)\n|\n|-\n|2019\n| ''[[Mosley (film)|Mosley]]''\n| Warnie (voice)\n|\n|}\n\n=== Television ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! Notes\n|-\n| 1974\n| ''[[Fall of Eagles]]''\n| Zi